Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).

          Description

Interface Summary
IAeWsdlReference Container class for wsdl properties that are accessed via AeMutableServiceDesc.
 

Class Summary
AeAxisEngineConfiguration This is a reusable implementation of the WSDDEngineConfiguration object.
AeAxisPrincipal Principal wrapper for Axis AuthenticatedUser principal
AeCatalogHelper Servlet designed to provide the WSDL which is part of a BPR deployment.
AeCatalogServlet Servlet designed to provide the WSDL which is part of a BPR deployment.
AeHandler The base handler for web services under an Axis framework.
AeMessages Accessor class for externalized strings
AeMutableServiceDesc A ServiceDesc impl that delegates access to its wsdl related properties to an IAeWsdlReference.
AeServiceDesc Custom Active Endpoints Service Description implementation.
AeWsdlReferenceTracker Adds IAeWsdlReference instances as IAeCatalogListener objects to the wsdl catalog on registration.
AeWsdlTrimmer Utility class that removes all WSDL elements which do not pertain to this service deployment.
AeWsdlTrimmer.AeImportUrl Utility class for formatting the "fixed up" import urls for wsdl and schemas.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.axis Description

Root package for the Active Endpoints Runtime for Axis (rtaxis).

Provides an implementation for an Active Endpoints Axis provider.
